snippet.title: Pyrotechnica gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Pyrotechnica, Dos PC game produced by Psygnosis in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/pyrotechnica/4798/
Flying around trying to shoot things in this tricky 3D Descent-style shooter.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
